to just talk to Vince and--

00:45.962 --> 00:47.297
Unh-unh.

00:47.380 --> 00:49.841
- I'm just saying--
- Unh!

00:49.924 --> 00:51.134
You forgave Tina.

00:51.217 --> 00:53.094
