to me, brown sugar.

07:31.617 --> 07:33.202
Buy you a drink?

07:33.286 --> 07:35.872
I'm quite alright,
thank you.

07:35.955 --> 07:38.457
Margarita, no salt?

07:38.541 --> 07:40.376
Alright.

07:40.459 --> 07:43.963
A free drink's
a free drink, brown sugar.

07:44.046 --> 07:45.882
Okay, so let's find
a nice place to lay out

07:45.965 --> 07:47.925
and forget about these
few horrible weeks.

07:48.009 --> 07:49.218
Ooh, what about next
to that guy?

07:49.302 --> 07:50.970
'He's totally my type.'

07:53.181 --> 07:55.725
Excuse me?

07:55.808 --> 07:57.518
Are these chairs taken?

08:02.481 --> 08:03.566
Oh, my God.

08:03.649 --> 08:06.110
