08:24.212 --> 08:26.547
Hey, Val,
you missed a real rush.

08:26.631 --> 08:29.759
So, how was your date
with Chris?

08:29.842 --> 08:31.093
Have you ever been
on one of those dates

08:31.177 --> 08:33.638
