I'm sorry.

08:52.156 --> 08:55.201
Yeah, I couldn't pull that one
off with a straight face.

08:55.284 --> 08:57.036
So you were boring, saying?

08:58.287 --> 08:59.956
Well, maybe this will
keep you up.

09:00.039 --> 09:02.291
