happen again, but it did.

09:30.027 --> 09:31.153
And I made out!

09:31.237 --> 09:32.655
[both laughing]

09:33.698 --> 09:35.449
[upbeat music]

09:39.120 --> 09:40.997
Are you sure you don't wanna
put on some sunscreen, dude?

09:41.080 --> 09:44.667
Oh, no thanks, I don't need it.
I have a nice base tan.

09:44.750 --> 09:46.043
Really. Huh.

09:46.127 --> 09:47.545
'Cause NASA just called
and said they could see

09:47.628 --> 09:49.005
