11:23.182 --> 11:25.684
Sorry.
It was an accident.

11:25.768 --> 11:27.937
Oh. Was it?

11:28.020 --> 11:29.397
Of course it was.

11:29.480 --> 11:31.315
What do you think,
I did that on purpose?

11:31.399 --> 11:33.859
Okay, looks like you two
are kind of causing a scene here

11:33.943 --> 11:36.112
