and you forgave her.

12:33.794 --> 12:34.837
What's the difference?

12:34.920 --> 12:36.172
The difference is,
I thought that maybe

12:36.255 --> 12:38.466
there would be a time
when you and I would..

12:38.549 --> 12:39.592
You know what?
Forget it.

12:39.675 --> 12:40.801
